{{#if hasTailwind}}
- Use Tailwind utilities first; limit `@apply` to repeatable design tokens.
{{/if}}
{{#if hasCSSModules}}
- Name modules `*.module.css`; prefer BEM-like class names scoped by file.
{{/if}}
{{#if hasCSSInJS}}
- Co-locate styles with components; avoid dynamic style objects in hot paths.
{{/if}}
{{#if hasSass}}
- Prefer variables/mixins for tokens; avoid deep selector nesting.
{{/if}}
{{#if hasVanillaExtract}}
- Define themes and contracts in `.css.ts` files; avoid inline sprinkles in loops.
{{/if}}
{{#if hasUnoCSS}}
- Prefer attributify/shortcuts configured in `uno.config` over one-off magic strings.
{{/if}}
